<p>Power plays are when you want your strongest skaters on the ice. But who do the Wild want on the ice during their power plays? Who do they want on the ice when they are on even strength?</p>
<p>The answer is Kirill Kaprizov. Kaprizov is the man you want on the ice when you are at an advantage or even strength. His even strength goals are significantly higher than many other wingers. When you see his power play goals, it is still all about him. The top 3 highest power play goals scored were by Kaprizov in his 2022, 2023 and 2024 season. He is the skater who can find the back of the net on an advantage or at even strength.</p>
<p>His name continues to pop up.</p>
